%% wtsagnt — Teacher Assistant Voice-WhatsApp Workflow
%% Source: Senthil (project owner), shared 2026-05-13
%% This is the FULL real-development target. The 2026-05-13 prototype builds a stripped
%% subset of this (no STT, no WhatsApp, no Drive, no rework loop, no distribution).
%% See: docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-13-wtsagnt-prototype-design.md

flowchart TD
    A[Teacher sends Voice Note via WhatsApp]
    B[Speech-to-Text Engine]
    C[Intent & Requirement Extraction Agent]
    D[Prompt Engineering Agent]
    E[Orchestrator Agent]
    F[Content Generation LLM - PPT]
    G[Assessment Generator - MCQ]
    H[Content Generation LLM - Ready Reckoner PDF]
    I[Format to Microsoft PPT]
    J[Format to PDF]
    K[File Packaging Agent]
    L[Upload to Google Drive]
    M[Notification Agent]
    N[Send WhatsApp Message:<br/>Task Completed + Drive Link]
    O{Teacher Response?}
    P[Approval Agent]
    Q[Selective File Distribution Agent]
    R[Upload to Google Classroom]
    S[Fetch Student Email IDs]
    T[Email Notification Agent]
    U[Send Email with Materials]
    V[Final WhatsApp Notification:<br/>Task Completed]

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    E --> G
    E --> H
    F --> I
    G --> I
    H --> J
    I --> K
    J --> K
    K --> L
    L --> M
    M --> N
    N --> O
    O -- "Changes Required" --> C
    O -- "Approved" --> P
    P --> Q
    Q --> R
    Q --> S
    S --> T
    T --> U
    U --> V
